  <brief_title>DS vs SIPS-Bariatric Surgery Comparasion</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Single Anastomosis, 300 cm Loop, Duodenal Switch (SIPS) Results in Less Nutritional Deficiencies Than the Standard Duodenal Switch (DS) Operation: A Multicenter, Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
