  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to answer the question of whether the single anastomosis, 300 cm
      loop, duodenal switch (SIPS) is an equally effective, safe, simpler operation with less
      nutritional and surgical risks than the standard duodenal switch (DS) operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
